<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-environment-food-rural-affairs> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We are responsible for improving and protecting the environment. We aim to grow a green economy and sustain thriving rural communities. We also support our world-leading food, farming and fishing industries. Defra is a ministerial department, supported by 34 agencies and public bodies ."@en .
